name: Unidentified_Twi%27lek_Jedi_(New_Sith_Wars)
content: A female Twi'lek Jedi traveled behind enemy lines with Vannar Treece's volunteer squad of Jedi to help abandoned worlds in the Republic. In 1032 BBY, she participated in Operation Influx, an ill-fated Jedi mission to disrupt baradium production in the Daimanate, a Sith princedom in the Grumani sector ruled by the Sith Lord Daiman. During the Raid on Chelloa, the Twi'lek Jedi was killed when another Sith Lord named Odion attacked Squatter's Hill with a kinetic corruptor. The sole Jedi survivor was the Jedi Knight Kerra Holt, who played an important role in the Chelloan affair.
